Class AlluxioMasterRestServiceHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • alluxio.master.AlluxioMasterRestServiceHandler

  • @NotThreadSafe
 @Path(value="master")
 @Produces(value="application/json")
public final class AlluxioMasterRestServiceHandler
extends Object
    This class is a REST handler for requesting general master information.
